# Code Style & Formatting

- Do not reformat unrelated files.
- Keep changes minimal and scoped to the request.
- Prefer ESLint for correctness and Prettier for formatting (don't fight the formatter).
- If adding config, keep it standard and minimal (avoid niche rule sets unless needed).

**Formatting Rules:**
